channel.title: Signlink.java help, PLEEEEASE?
channel.description:
When I compile, I get this - .\sign\signlink.java:146: findcachedir() is already defined in sign.signlink public static final String findcachedir() ^ Note: client.java uses unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . .
Any idea why?
